# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Gaffer needs NO API keys and NO accounts. This is the whole point:
# all inference is on-device (@qvac/sdk) or on a peer you trust.
# Every variable below is OPTIONAL tuning.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Model source override (optional) ─────────────────────────────
# Where the QVAC engine loads its GGUF from. Accepts:
#   • a local path            /models/llama-3.2-1b-q4.gguf
#   • an http(s) URL          (first download only — match day needs none)
#   • a pear:// link          printed by `node scripts/seed_model.js`
# Default: the SDK's LLAMA_3_2_1B_INST_Q4_0 constant.
# GAFFER_MODEL_SRC=pear://<drive-key>/llama-3.2-1b-q4.gguf

# ── Debug (optional) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Print full stack traces from cli.js on fatal errors.
# GAFFER_DEBUG=1
